  "instructions": [
    "Cook the chicken breast in a pan at medium heat until fully cooked. Set aside.",
    "In the same pan, sauté the diced onion and minced garlic until softened.",
    "Add the Syrian curry powder, gentle curry powder, and spiced cumin to the pan. Stir for 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked chicken back into the pan and stir well to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Warm the tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by spooning the chicken mixture onto a tortilla and topping with shredded cheese and cilantro.",
